--- 
title  : Erbside
summary: ERB-based Inline Templating
contact: trans <transfire@gmail.com>
suite  : rubyworks
authors: Thomas Sawyer
created: 2009-07-15

description:
  Erbside is a simple project-oriented erb-based inline template system.
  Inline templates make it easy to do basic code generation without
  the need for duplicate files.

requires:
  - facets
  - pom
  - ko (test)

